If... If I don't make it in time...

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.990
I'll end up disappointing Kitagawa-san, when she's really looking forward to this.

00:00:43.230 --> 00:00:46.720
Anyway, as soon as I get home, I'll make the patterns, then start cutting...

00:00:47.250 --> 00:00:49.730
How long does the cutting take?

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:54.460
I'm not dealing with parts that I can just cut in straight lines, like a kimono.

00:00:54.460 --> 00:00:56.520
Will I even be done in two or three days?

00:00:57.430 --> 00:00:59.530
It's no use. There's not enough time.

00:01:00.740 --> 00:01:02.540
I feel like I'm losing my mind...

00:01:02.540 --> 00:01:05.420
"Slippery Girls" had started to violate Wakana.

00:02:37.010 --> 00:02:40.010
Episode 4
Are These Your Girlfriend's?

00:02:40.820 --> 00:02:41.840
I'm home.

00:02:42.330 --> 00:02:44.470
Hey, welcome back.

00:02:44.730 --> 00:02:47.600
You're home pretty late today.

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:50.980
Oh, sorry. I forgot to call you.

00:02:50.980 --> 00:02:53.980
Handmade Hobby Shop Yuzawaya
I was out shopping with a friend.

00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:57.810
With a friend? I see, I see!

00:02:57.810 --> 00:02:59.570
So, what did you buy?

00:02:59.570 --> 00:03:01.570
A CD? Maybe some books?

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:03.460
Huh?

00:03:03.570 --> 00:03:05.660
Lovely Legs Stockings

00:03:11.180 --> 00:03:13.100
Huh? Gramps?!

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:21.460
Wacchan!

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:26.030
Miori-neechan... Sorry to call you over here.

00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:28.090
It's fine. How's Grandpa?

00:03:28.090 --> 00:03:30.060
They're putting a compress on him right now.

00:03:30.580 --> 00:03:31.620
I see.

00:03:31.620 --> 00:03:33.920
Thankfully, he didn't hit a really bad spot.

00:03:34.570 --> 00:03:37.070
We'll get you some painkillers.

00:03:37.370 --> 00:03:39.620
Please take care.

00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:42.400
Sorry for the trouble. Thanks for everything.

00:03:43.010 --> 00:03:44.060
Gramps!

00:03:44.060 --> 00:03:45.020
Hey.

00:03:45.850 --> 00:03:47.350
For crying out loud, Grandpa!

00:03:47.350 --> 00:03:50.910
Hey, Miori. What're you doing here?

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:50.910
Take your time.

00:03:51.140 --> 00:03:53.580
Don't give me that!

00:03:53.580 --> 00:03:54.920
I was really worried!

00:03:57.170 --> 00:03:58.050
Nurses' Station

00:03:57.330 --> 00:03:59.660
You need to stay in bed for two weeks, don't you?

00:03:59.660 --> 00:04:03.190
Dad wanted you to stay at our place until you get better.

00:04:03.190 --> 00:04:05.460
That's why I came to get you.

00:04:05.460 --> 00:04:09.060
Why not take them up on that? Uncle's house is closer to the hospital, too.

00:04:09.380 --> 00:04:11.520
Plus, we have a car.

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:15.100
I see. I hope I'm not gonna be a burden.

00:04:15.440 --> 00:04:17.990
Wacchan, you should spend the night at our place, too.

00:04:17.990 --> 00:04:19.700
We'll put out a futon for you.

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:20.440
Okay.

00:04:21.200 --> 00:04:23.610
I'll bring by some spare clothes tomorrow.

00:04:23.610 --> 00:04:26.760
Thanks, and sorry about this. Also...

00:04:27.930 --> 00:04:30.490
Bring me my brushes.

00:04:30.490 --> 00:04:31.220
Huh?

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:34.540
Okay.

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:37.540
Maybe we should take you to an acupuncturist, too.

00:04:37.870 --> 00:04:41.550
Yeah... Ow... Are you okay?

00:04:41.550 --> 00:04:45.070
All this shaking's got me shook up.

00:04:45.070 --> 00:04:46.430
Oh, come on.

00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:51.520
I see. So that's why you weren't at school yesterday.

00:04:52.380 --> 00:04:53.230
Yes.

00:04:53.550 --> 00:04:56.900
I'll be stopping by my cousin's place again today to see how he's doing.

00:04:57.500 --> 00:04:59.070
You must be really worried.

00:04:59.530 --> 00:05:02.280
I hope your grandpa feels better soon.

00:05:03.430 --> 00:05:04.490
Yes...

00:05:08.210 --> 00:05:11.620
Gojo-kun, let me know if there's anything I can help you with.

00:05:11.620 --> 00:05:14.290
Believe it or not, I can cook and stuff.

00:05:15.010 --> 00:05:16.430
Kitagawa-san...

00:05:17.320 --> 00:05:19.010
Thank you very much.

00:05:19.010 --> 00:05:20.940
I'll be fine, though.

00:05:20.940 --> 00:05:22.710
I-I see.

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:25.880
Oh, hey. Let's exchange contact info.

00:05:25.880 --> 00:05:28.470
It'd be best if we can reach each other if something happens.

00:05:28.990 --> 00:05:29.840
Right?

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:34.850
Sure.

00:05:40.430 --> 00:05:43.950
I wasn't able to work on the outfit yesterday or the day before.

00:05:44.750 --> 00:05:46.080
I need to today, even just a little.

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:51.950
Oh, yeah! The wig's been cut, so I brought it to give to you.

00:05:53.420 --> 00:05:54.410
Gojo-kun?

00:05:54.410 --> 00:05:56.210
Oh, sorry.

00:05:57.210 --> 00:06:00.790
Man, midterms are next week.

00:06:01.150 --> 00:06:02.880
Talk about exhausting.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:06.720
Not to mention, I'm the type that just crams the night before.

00:06:04.010 --> 00:06:08.880
I-I totally forgot... That's right... We have tests!

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:08.880
Are you the type that always studies, Gojo-kun?

